data.description: Welcome to your move-in-ready waterfront home in the desirable Buckhead Ridge community! This remarkable 2-story home offers a waterfront lifestyle, complete w/ a private boat ramp & canal-side dock, providing direct access to the picturesque Lake Okeechobee. Whether you're an avid fisherman, boater or simply seeking the tranquility of waterside living, this home offers it all. Features inc. waterfront happiness nestled on a fenced lot & peaceful canal w/ direct lake access; a tastefully renovated interior w/ a kitchen that shines w/ new stainless steel appliances & Corian countertops & all new appliances inc. water heater, washer & dryer; the main floor features new wood laminate flooring, open living space. Dont miss your chance to own a move-in-ready home in Buckhead Ridge!
